window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Dragons. Faeries. Magic. Rednecks.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>This ain't your daddy's fairy tale. Unless your daddy was a defensive end for the Georgia Bulldogs. In the third installment of the Bubba in Fairyland saga, Bubba and his band of merry men and women are still on the hunt for his missing sister. Their journey this time brings them to the Summer Court, home of Titania and Oberon, neither of whom are fans of giant rednecks with giant guns.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Top find Bubba's missing sister, they have to find a dragon. But first, Bubba has to find his way out of this patch of woods without getting everybody killed!</p>"; 
